Preesha..
- Tidak!  Ibu akan ikut denganku!

00:17:49.635 --> 00:17:51.384
Preesha dengarkan aku.
- Rudraksh!

00:17:51.427 --> 00:17:53.011
Dia masih kecil, biarkan dia bermain..
- Rudraksh..

00:17:53.136 --> 00:17:54.384
Saaransh, dengarkan aku.
- Ini sangat penting..

00:17:54.427 --> 00:17:55.510
Tinggalkan aku!

